definition: to offer tribute/to pay tribute that a vassal owes to his suzerain
to go forward/to advance/to go in/to enter/to put in/to submit/to take in/to admit/(math.) base of a number system/classifier for sections in a building or residential compound

sentences.english: And so the Moabites became David's servants, and brought gifts.
sentences.chinese: 摩押人就歸服大衛，給他進貢。

sentences.english: And he smote Moab; and the Moabites became David's servants, and brought gifts.
sentences.chinese: 又攻打摩押，摩押人就歸服大衛，給他進貢。

sentences.english: David also defeated the Moabites, and they became subject to him and brought tribute.
sentences.chinese: 又攻打摩押，摩押人就歸服大衛，給他進貢。

sentences.english: The time since the Song Dynasty people have used it as a tribute of the imperial court.
sentences.chinese: 自宋朝的時分就有人用它作爲貢品進貢朝廷。

sentences.english: She who was a princess among the provinces Has become tributary .
sentences.chinese: 先前在諸省中爲王后的，現在成了進貢的。

sentences.english: And the king Ahasuerus laid a tribute upon the land, and upon the isles of the sea.
sentences.chinese: 亞哈隨魯王使旱地，和海島的人民都進貢。

sentences.english: He once presented litchis from here as a tribute to Emperor Tang Xuanzong's concubine, Yang Guifei.
sentences.chinese: 他曾經把這裏的荔枝進貢給唐玄宗的妃子楊貴妃喫。

sentences.english: She who was queen among the provinces has now become a slave.
sentences.chinese: 先前在諸省中爲王后的，現在成爲進貢的。

sentences.english: Slinging is not allowed until the 30th minute of the game.
sentences.chinese: 進貢在遊戲開始的前30分鐘被禁止。

sentences.english: Egypt for many years and pay…
sentences.chinese: 第二，他們多年都是埃及的進貢國。

sentences.english: Give Carmen the tribute for captain Red.
sentences.chinese: 給卡門進貢爲紅色上尉。

sentences.english: China's leaders can no longer make such offer.
sentences.chinese: 中國的領導人沒法再進貢這麼多中國女人了。

sentences.english: This is the first instance recorded in history about the tribute - paying song and dance of Zangke.
sentences.chinese: 這是第一次見於正史的關於牂牁進貢歌舞的記載。

sentences.english: Estonians made offerings to local fertility and thunder gods.
sentences.chinese: 愛沙尼亞人向當地的收成和雷神進貢。

sentences.english: I believe for a business to succeed, it has to pay tribute to Buddha.
sentences.chinese: 我相信一個事業要成功，就必須拜佛進貢。

sentences.english: The tribute ended with the occupation of Qatar by the Ottoman Turks in 1872.
sentences.chinese: 進貢在1872年奧斯曼土耳其佔領卡塔爾時結束。
